As South Africa bids farewell to the mother of the nation, EWN looks back on a remarkable life in service of the struggle. JOHANNESBURG - Winnie-Madikizela Mandela is being remembered across South Africa this week in a series of memorial services and events. Ahead of her special funeral on Saturday 14 May, at Orlando Stadium in Soweto, EWN looks back at her remarkable life. LISTEN: Madikizela-Mandela 1936 - 2018 